Kau harus mati.

692
00:44:10,425 --> 00:44:11,635
Setiap hari.

693
00:44:11,926 --> 00:44:13,886
Sampai Omega hancur.

694
00:44:26,691 --> 00:44:28,111
Pertama-tama...

695
00:44:28,401 --> 00:44:30,281
